<h2>Custom styling for ordered lists with CSS3</h2>


<h3>Why this?</h3>
<!-- BEGIN paragraph -->
<div class="tech_paragraph">
A friend who's administrating the content of a website called me 
recently asking for an easy way to change the numbering of the
bibliography notes for an article.<br/>
<br/>
<b>Screenshot:</b><br/>
<img src="/img/Screenshot from 2016-01-29 132723_A.png" width="316" height="213" alt="Screenshot bibliography notes" /><br/>
<br/>
